<p begin='00:01:23.350' end='00:01:27.120' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; THE BEGINNING OF THE<br/>ATLANTIC HURRICANE SEASON.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:27.154' end='00:01:28.155' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt;&gt; HURRICANE SEASON.</span></p>
