<p begin='00:01:31.658' end='00:01:34.194' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>EARLIER EVERY YEAR BECAUSE<br/>THANKS TO GLOBAL WARMING IT</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:34.228' end='00:01:34.962' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>NEVER REALLY ENDS.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:34.995' end='00:01:37.664' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>(LAUGHTER)<br/>BUT HERE&apos;S MY NUMBER ONE</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:37.698' end='00:01:39.099' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>HURRICANE SEASON SAFETY TIP.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:39.099' end='00:01:43.370' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>IF YOU LIVE ANYWHERE ON THE<br/>COAST FROM GALVESTON, TEXAS,</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:43.403' end='00:01:47.574' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>TO WILMINGTON, NORTH<br/>CAROLINA, DON&apos;T.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:47.608' end='00:01:50.978' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>(LAUGHTER)<br/>NOW WE&apos;VE JUST FOUND OUT</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:51.011' end='00:01:53.847' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>WE&apos;VE JUST FOUND OUT, FOLKS,<br/>WHEN IT COMES TO HURRICANES</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:53.881' end='00:01:56.116' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THERE IS A NEW NAME FOR<br/>DANGER.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:56.149' end='00:01:57.217' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>AND IT&apos;S GIRLY.</span></p>
